+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|           Semtech SX1278 firmware for STM32F0                               |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

This firmware currently supports the following Semtech LoRa product:
	- SX1278
		- LoRa modem (application default)

1. Introduction
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The SX12xx drivers are included in a project made for the STM32F0 platform.	Currently my development hardware is STM32F0 discovery kit (STM32F00308-DISCO) plus SFM-1L SX1278 LoRa module.	

1. Version history
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<V1.0.0> - This is original project from ST which SX1278 radio driver is not ported.